item.description: Welcome to Wind of Fate Productions. We are based in Brandon, Manitoba, Canada. We are not a set team, group, or company, we are independent, sometimes collaborators, that are striving to hone our artistic crafts. Whether it be Filmmaking, Poetry, or Painting, Scrapbooking, Music, or Design, we are all working towards excellence. Happy to see the Wind of Fate has brought you here.
